name: HGL Polo
description:
I love polos. I HAD to make one of my own. Embroidered logo stitched with love so treat this shirt well.

As always the polo is made from the softest ringspun cotton around.
Go through the pictures to see the detail on the embroidered HGL logo. 

Each shirt comes with 3 stickers and a hang tag with additional info about the design.

name: End in Disaster
description:
Everyone lies. Everyone hurts people they love. It happens. We put ourselves in situations sometimes where we know it will come crashing down on us, but the ride to downfall is so grand....it makes it all worth it. Please enjoy your life. Do what feels good because tomorrow may never come.

Printed on super soft ringspun cotton. The ink is all waterbased which means it feels like the ink isnt there.

Each shirt comes with 3 stickers and a hang tag with additional info about the design.

name: Balance
description:
Over the years ive done good things and bad things to people i love. Even to people i love to hate. I would ask myself, "Jayarr." "Why would you do something you know is wrong?" The answer is simple. Its all to get closer to the middle. Everything we do at any given second is all moving towards a search for balance. Thats it.

Printed on 100% ringspun super soft cotton. This shirt was tailored to be "inside out" so dont freak out when you get the thing and it looks wrong.

Each shirt comes with 3 stickers and a hang tag with additional info about the design.

name: HGL College
description:
I didnt go to college. Well i did for a bit, but then i was homeless for like...the first few months of my freshman year...so i dropped out. Anyway, I took the next 7 years figuring out who i was. Watching people spend $200,000 on schooling just to find out that THAT wasnt what they wanted to do for a career. Now im 28, and i do what i love. No college. Thats why i made this shirt.

Printed on a thicker, yet soft ringspun cotton shirt. There is a "yoke" on the top of the shirt going all the way around to make it look kind of like a jersey. Youll see.

Each shirt comes with 3 stickers and a hang tag with additional info about the design.

name: Super HGL
description:
I am a huge gamer. I have 3 videogame based tattoos. This shirt is an homage to the most recognizable videogame character ever.

Printed on super soft ringspun cotton. The ink is all waterbased which means it feels like the ink isnt there.

Each shirt comes with 3 stickers and a hang tag with additional info about the design.
